    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The user unsheathes his weapons and makes a single attack with the hilt at his highest attack bonus. On a successful hit, the target suffers weapon damage + 3d6 as non-lethal damage. If this would provoke a Fort save against unconsciousness, use the Fort save of this technique instead.<br><br>The user's held weapon will be left unsheathed wh en this technique is completed.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Kenjutsu: Iaido (2)</p>\n<p><b>Material Focus:</b> The user's h eld weapon with a solid sheath.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The second and fourth steps of mastery in this technique increase the save DC of this technique by 1.</p>\n",
